snippet.title: Dark Crown - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Reclaim your kingdom from the darkness! Gather your army and use powerful magics to defeat the forces of an evil that lurks in the shadows in this chess-like roguelite deckbuilder.

Join our Discord to play our pre-alpha build now!
https://discord.gg/pHCtmgdZhs

Follow us for more!
https://twitter.com/HyperDiveStudio
